title: New: Kwabs – Something Right
content:
Yet another SOHN produced beauty from one of the voices of the year.

Kwabs. has been tearing up the UK airwaves as of late, and his newest track, Something Right, which saw it’s debut last night, is sure to do the same. His boldest yet, it’s powerful, overly dramatic and destined to cast a chilling silence amongst packed out venues across the country.
